                                 Version 2.5
                                 June 01, 1995


Until> Welcome to UNTIL

Until>

__________________________________________________________________


Stack contents are displayed in the upper right hand corner of the
screen every time through the Outer Interpreter loop (DOS only). Type
bye to exit Until and return to DOS.

__________________________________________________________________

UNTIL.BIN

The following is the default listing for what is sealed into
UNTIL.BIN.

(  until.app )

: hello
   ." Welcome to UNTIL" cr cr
   ;

-1 constant true
 0 constant false

: d.           ( d --- )
   drop .
   ;

: >here                 ( 'string --- )  ( copy string to here )
   here 20 0 fill
   count here swap cmove
   ;

true null_strings
false string_returns

hello



